  main
    section.about-us__section
      .about-us.about-us__row#mission
        .about-us__title
          h2.secondary-heading Our Mission
        .about-us__desc
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            To help millions of peope all over the world create wealth, with the speed of the internet by leveraging on the power of the global financial market (GFM).
            
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            We believe that decentralised cryptocurrencies, like Bitcoin, Ethereum etc.. will revolutionise the way the world views, and uses money.
            
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            We are part of pioneering a new financial system being built in real time, and we believe that this new global system will accelerate humanity for generations to come.
            
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            As early innovators in this industry, we feel it’s our duty to bring this knowledge and excitement to the world.
            
      .about-us__row
        .about-us__title
          h2.secondary-heading Our Focus
        .about-us__desc
          p.secondary-desc
            strong Our focused businesses are
          h3.tertiary-heading E-commerce
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            We help you to start your own e-commerce (Drop shipping, mini import and affiliate marketing) business. With this you can invest and earn salary for life.
            
          h3.tertiary-heading Cryptocurrency
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            SU1trade exchange is a semi-automatic platform which sells, buys and exchanges crypto ‘currency’ units online. Fee is moderate. We are always open to negotiations. Our customers positive reviews confirm the lowest exchange rate and high quality of our work.
            
          h3.tertiary-heading E-Trading
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            We educate on forex, oil, metals, commodities and trading in the global financial market (GFM). We link you to professional traders that can manage your account for you. You earn 28% on your investment monthly on our Funds Management Program or 17% every month for five(5) months on our Lending Investment Program.
            
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            You can earn and learn with SU1trade focused businesses, Which is the ultimate vehicle that will bring you financial freedom, respect, dignity, and the power to change your life.
            
      .about-us__row#team
        .about-us__title
          h2.secondary-heading Our Team
        .about-us__desc
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            Here is the team behind SU1trade. You can contact is on our social media channel. We’d love to chat with you.
            
          h2.secondary-heading MEET SU1trade TEAM
          .our-team__fig
            .our-team
              figure
                .figinfo
                  h3.tertiary-heading Sherif Ogehie
                  p.secondary-desc CEO & Founder
                .figphoto
                  img(src="assets/sherif-ogerie-00.png", alt="Photo of Sherif Ogehie")
              figure
                .figinfo
                  h3.tertiary-heading Promise Mbagwu
                  p.secondary-desc Social Media Manager
                .figphoto
                  img(src="assets/promise-mbagwu-00.png", alt="Photo of Promise Mbagwu")
      .about-us__row#contact-us
        .about-us__title
          h2.secondary-heading Contact Us
        .about-us__desc
          h2.secondary-heading
            | Contact us for
            br
            | one-on-one help?

          .about-us__btn
            a(href="#contact-number")
              button.btn--primary.btn--medium.
                
                Contact Us for one-on-one help
                
          h2.secondary-heading Customer Service
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            Contact our customer service. We’re here to help.
            
          p.secondary-desc.
            
            Email sherif@su1trade.com or click the yellow button below.
            
          .about-us__btn
            a(href="mailto:sherif@su1trade.com?subject=I need help on how to Investment")
              button.btn--primary.btn--medium.
                
                Email Support
                
